    "id": "MEM-1773760535166",
    "text": "Akira dev team core is online",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:15:35.166Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773760636819",
    "text": "I’m thinking of building an app that tracks my sleeping pattern",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:17:16.819Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773760779393",
    "text": "User will need to enter/log their sleep cycle as well as their workouts and their daily routine so the app can have a better understanding, more information more food for the database right",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:19:39.393Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773760903542",
    "text": "Sleep cycle logging, and if they are up in the middle of the night they can’t log that also, when they are up for work or for the day they can’t log log their sleep quality.",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:21:43.542Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773760974532",
    "text": "They are looking start time and end time, I want them to have a good insight as to why they are not sleeping well or sleeping too much.\nAnyways let’s build it",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:22:54.532Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761020786",
    "text": "What’s the dev status",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:23:40.786Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761041364",
    "text": "Run the next task",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:24:01.364Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761098402",
    "text": "Review",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:24:58.402Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761134732",
    "text": "Start T2",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:25:34.732Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761240138",
    "text": "100% alert them about their unusual sleep patterns. \nNative time pick on mobile we can polish the UI later",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:27:20.138Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761286468",
    "text": "Delete this project",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:28:06.468Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761368853",
    "text": "Nope I want to completely delete this sleepsync project. Remember it but delete all files",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:29:28.853Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761425632",
    "text": "For now stand on idle",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:30:25.632Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761469315",
    "text": "Tetsuo shouldn’t have anything with the sleepsync anymore, I asked you to delete it",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:31:09.315Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761525429",
    "text": "All workers delete everything on sleepsync including their tasks on this project",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:32:05.429Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761614173",
    "text": "I’m decided not to pursue with this project, and with any future projects I don’t want any works to confuse this project with future works",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:33:34.173Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761683224",
    "text": "Completely wipe it, and clear all pending tasks regarding this project",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:34:43.224Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761726003",
    "text": "So there is nothing left on sleepsync?",
    "created_at": "2026-03-17T15:35:26.003Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "MEM-1773761754093",
    "text": "I want you to delete everything and forget everything on sleepsync",
